main event: A detailed report from Project Blue Book documenting a UFO sighting on July 29, 1964.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for two hours and the object was still visible., The object was described as spinning like a top and appeared to veer., The report indicates that the object was moving from east to southwest., There were no physical evidence or photographs associated with this sighting., A military intelligence officer stated that no analysis could be made from the information available.
sighted object: An unidentified flying object described as oval and very bright
witness description: A contractor looking out of a window from his bed.
